task.implementation:
The /factorial-monitor skill already polls job status. Add logic:
1. Track time each job has been in PENDING/STARTING state.
2. If any job exceeds 15 min in PENDING/STARTING:
   - Write outputs/experiment_status.txt with:
     TIMESTAMP: {now}
     STATUS: CAPACITY_CONSTRAINED
     PENDING_JOBS: {list}
     PENDING_DURATION: {minutes}
     REGIONS_TRIED: {list}
     SUGGESTION: Consider europe_us region config for US fallback
3. Update the file every 5 min while constraint persists.
4. Clear the file when jobs start running.
